In short, Gauche is distributed under so called "BSD license",
that is, as far as you retain the copyrignt notice and disclaimer below,
you can use, copy, modify and redistribute your modification freely.
The formal term is specified in each copyright notices.

A few files associated to autoconf and libtool in the distribution are
covered by GPL, but they have an exception so that I (and you) can
distribute them under BSD license.  See each file for the detailed term.


